nbi-degrees of a bi-homogeneous minimal generating set for A_{d1-2} and the\nnumber of singularities of multiplicity d1 which are on or infinitely near C.\nWe conclude with a table which translates between the bi-degrees of a\nbi-homogeneous minimal generating set for A and the configuration of\nsingularities of C in the case that the curve C has degree six.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Jan 2013 23:58:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2016 23:28:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-27"}
