ers, e.g., the probability that a user will call the $c_r$-th most\ncontact and the probability distribution of burst sizes. Our findings may\nenable a more detailed analysis of the huge body of data contained in the logs\nof massive users.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jan 2013 09:26:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-31"}
