d at LUNA, the effect of this weak flux\nof 2-3 MeV neutrons on well-shielded high-purity germanium detectors has been\nstudied in detail. Data have been taken at 280 and 400 keV alpha-beam energy\nand for comparison also using an americium-beryllium neutron source.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jan 2013 10:22:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-26"}
